      "title": "The Kota Escape: The Search in Kandy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lankan protesters have entered both the Presidential Secretariat and the Presidential Palace in Colombo. President Gotabaya Rajapaksa was not present in both the places.",
        "At the same time, the protestors have carried out fierce protests in front of the President's House in Kandy. There is also a tense situation."
